<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٤٣ - <span class="c4">[حَدَّثَنَا أَحْمَدُ بْنُ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ يَعْقُوبَ،]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنْ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">كَانَ نَقْشُ خَاتَمِ مُعَاوِيَةَ:</span> لا قُوَّةَ إِلا بِاللَّهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَكَانَ نَقْشُ <span class="c4">[خَاتَمِ]</span> يَزِيدَ بْنِ مُعَاوِيَةَ: آمَنْتُ بِاللَّهِ الْعَظِيمِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">وَكَانَ نَقْشُ خَاتَمِ مُعَاوِيَةَ بْنِ يَزِيدَ:</span> يَثِقُ بالله معاوية.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>